iosdofficial.name: IOSD Orientation
iosdofficial.details:
IOSD- International Organisation of Software development is now spreading its roots in our University. Started off as a group of Android techies, they have now reached a point where they organised the longest- techfest, largest Hackathon and was also recognised as the largest student organisation in Delhi-NCR.

The aim of IOSD is to provide a platform for development enthusiasts from over the country to enrich their skills via yielding projects, workshops, forums, etc. Team up together to build applications using different hybrid technologies and help them adapt to the industrial environment.

Jadavpur University buckle up and stay tuned for all these oppurtunities are coming to your doorstep.

iosdofficial.name: IOSD TechDay Summer 2018
iosdofficial.details:
Details at:
http://techday.iosd.tech/
Register for all events at:
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdQDTcX1EX8odhC0Kx0slv3wYrGVJYGJi2xV4he8YKEDDonYg/viewform

To boost the spirit of our beloved Freshers, IOSD has decided to organise one of a kind Techday, wherein having fun will be the major goal, because not only will we be having tech-related events, a huge part of the day would include non-tech and other fun activities to keep you all engrossed all day long. 
Techday would include the following events: 

### The Code Saga
A quarterly organised Coding Challenge exclusively designed for IOSD's Techday Series, aimed to test the interest of tech enthusiasts in the field of Competitive Coding.
 
### Introduction to Coding by Prateek Narang
A workshop so intellectual, it’ll awake the coder in you, with the Co-Founder of CODING BLOCKS, Mr. Prateek Narang to guide you on the fundamentals of coding.
 
### Winner Winner Chicken Dinner
IOSD Gaming introduces the talk of the town, to challenge your buddies into Player Unknowns Battlegrounds A.K.A. PUBG. #PubG
 
Techday will be held on 21st of August’18. Come along to learn while having fun at it.

Follow the most active organisation at:

https://www.instagram.com/iosdofficial/

https://www.twitch.tv/iosdofficial

iosdofficial.details:
Build your algo, run your code.

iosdofficial.name: MAIT Hacks | Impuse'18 IOSD MAIT
iosdofficial.details:
No talks, All actions!
Because Talk is cheap and truth can only be found in one place: the CODE!!!

IOSD-MAIT proudly presents

           MAIT HACKS
    
       36- hours hackathon 

Register today at:
http://impulseiosd.tech

Event details:
This will be a 2 round event. 

• Round 1: This is an online round. The participants will get two random keywords generated from the website on 7th March from 9 pm onwards. 
Project ideas should involve both the keywords. Ideas to be uploaded on the website before 12 pm of 8th March 2018.
Result will be announced on 6 pm on the same day.

• Round 2: Offline round. Selected teams from round 1 would have to demonstrate their working project  in the project pitching round. 

DATE: 9th March 
TIME: 9am onwards 
‎VENUE: Mini Audi ,MAIT

Prizes worth Rs 1 lakh up for grabs!!!, Cash prizes , internship and incubation offers, Certificates, .tech domains to everyone and much more.

The feeling of having implemented something innovative as part of a great team is priceless.
